cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a method to generate sample-specific filters for convolutional layers in CNNs, which is a topic related to computer vision (CV) and machine learning (ML). Therefore, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The method involves learning a set of coefficients to linearly combine base filters, which is a technique related to artificial intelligence (AI) and neural networks (NE). Finally, the proposed method is evaluated on image datasets, which is a topic related to multimedia (MM).
